## Uses

::READ (NaturalExpression, Identifier, NaturalName) FROM `language/grammar/index.art`.

## Primitive: List

**Id**: `list`

**Name**: List

**Kind**: Primitive

**Purpose:** Defines ordered collections of items.

**ValueType:**

```ts
type PrimitiveList = {
  items: T;
};
```

**Value:**

```ts
type PrimitiveListValue = {
  items: T[];
};
```
